title: Bobby and Amy’s Dentist On The Craziest Things People Said On Laughing Gas + BIG TWIST in Phone Screener Abby’s Texting with Fireman + Our Relationships with Spouse’s Best Friends and Our In-Laws
itunes:title: Bobby and Amy’s Dentist On The Craziest Things People Said On Laughing Gas + BIG TWIST in Phone Screener Abby’s Texting with Fireman + Our Relationships with Spouse’s Best Friends and Our In-Laws
description:
Bobby and Amy’s dentist humors us in our strange questions like Is it ok to use floss pics instead of floss?, the craziest things people say when they are on laughing gas, what if someone's breath is really bad?? Phone Screener Abby shares that there has been a major twist in her situation with the fireman. We shared updates on our relationships with our spouse’s best friends and our In-Laws.
